I had got this huge bump on my Lower lip. It had happened due to lip bite. Over a period of time it grew out very very big. I had consulted other dentist who had prescribed medicines but nothing helped. Finally I consulted Dr. Gaurav Goel. He advised me to immediately get it removed. He and his senior surgeon removed the big chunk successfully. It was as complicated process but they really managed well without distorting my lip. To my surprise the process was Painless. Recovery was also smooth. A big thank you.

Me and my wife visited doctor Gaurav on 7th Oct’19. Doctor was unfriendly and rude during the treatment. When asked over the advice to have only 2 fillings out of three teeth with problem, he appeared rude to answer.
When asked over the longivity of the fillings, he said there is no minimum or maximum limit. Well that was ok, but the way he responded it seem as if he is totally unconcerned even if the fillings go out very next day.

My wife had a tooth decay and paining a little and asked him to check. He checked and told there is no option but to take teeth out surgically. When asked about another alternative, he said No. **** ***** ** ******* ******* ** **** **** **** ** ** *** **** ******

My last visit with doctor around 2 years back was very good and he appeared quite helping. This time it looked completely opposite.
